(1) Download the pos project from git.
(2) Go to the file: application.properties.
(3) Change the following lines of "application.properties".:
    spring.datasource.username=root (Use your database username)
    spring.datasource.password=root (Use your database password)
    spring.jpa.hibernate.ddl-auto = update (Use create for the 1st time. Then you can use update.)

(4) Create a database named "pos" in your system.
(5) To run the project select Application file. Click right button. Select "Run 'Application'".
(6) Go to your database. in role table add 2 rows.
    id=1 role=ADMIN
    id=2 role=USER

(7) Go to browser. The url is: http://localhost:8080/login
(8) To login, you need to make an user 1st. So, Click the "Go To Registration Page" button in the upper side of the page.
(9) Then with the registered user login in the system.
